                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
                    Add each participant with their salary or rate, set the
                    duration, and the calculator multiplies each person’s hourly
                    cost by the meeting length, then sums everything. You can
                    also run the live ticker to see the cost accumulate while
                    you are in the meeting.
